FT  09 MAY 91 / UK Company News: Little change at London Atlantic
London Atlantic Investment Trust yesterday announced a net asset value of
79.7p per share at its March 31 year end.
The figure represented a marginal decline from the previous year's 81.6p.
The trust, which specialises in smaller companies and is 55 per cent-owned
by 3i, reported net revenue of Pounds 1.32m (Pounds 1.17m) for the year.
Earnings per share worked through at 2.9p (2.57p) and a recommended final
distribution of 2.08p lifts the total by 0.3p to 2.8p.
